prompts.frontCover: Charming and humorous cartoon-style illustration for a birthday card front. Two endearing cartoon pangolins are the central focus. The first pangolin, on the left, is playfully curled into a roly-poly ball, looking up with a mischievous and joyful expression. The second pangolin, on the right, is standing on its hind legs, wearing a tiny, festive birthday party hat, and tenderly poking the curled-up pangolin with one claw as if to say "boop!". The entire scene is set against a clean, off-white background. The pangolins are encircled by a beautiful, delicate, and lush botanical wreath made of watercolor monstera leaves, vibrant green ferns, and small, whimsical white and soft pink flowers. The style is flat 2D vector art with a soft, hand-drawn feel, clean lines, and a warm, natural color palette. In the center of the wreath, above the pangolins, is the text "Happy Birthday, Lao Lao!" written in a beautiful, elegant, yet readable handwritten cursive script in a dark teal color. The overall composition is balanced, delightful, and full of personality.
